
*  The configuration option to mount the storage partition at boot time does not work

*  The format script lets you set up a null-password storage, but mount will fail mounting it.

*  Trasparent TOR routing isn't working. Tor proxying with Firefox and Bitcoin works fine.

*  Switching off the PC or pulling out the USB drive while bitcoin is working can cause the blockchain to become corrupt, requiring you to delete the blockchain file or formatting the storage.

*  Blockchain downloader script doesn't support resume, and deletes the stored blockchain (if any) as soon as it's started.
